  "architecture_summary": "VisualBERT is a BERT-based Transformer that jointly processes text tokens and image region features as input embeddings, using self-attention to implicitly align words and bounding regions. It is pre-trained on COCO captions with masked language modeling and sentence-image prediction, then task-specifically pre-trained and fine-tuned for vision-and-language tasks.",
